relevant_findings.general: Alert and in no acute distress.
relevant_findings.eyes: Anicteric, normal conjunctivae. Pupils equally round.
relevant_findings.ent: Ears and nose without visible erythema, masses, or trauma. Oropharynx without visible lesion, erythema, or exudate.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Heart regular, no murmur, no S3, no S4. No peripheral edema.
relevant_findings.respiratory: Lungs clear to auscultation with good air movement bilaterally. Breathing is non-labored.
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: Abdomen soft, obese habitus, non-distended, RUQ tender to palpation. Bowel sounds present. No hepatomegaly or splenomegaly.
relevant_findings.musculoskeletal: Neck supple, moves all extremities, strength grossly full and symmetric bilaterally in all limbs.
relevant_findings.neurological: Face symmetric, gaze conjugate with EOMI, speech fluent. Sensation to light touch grossly intact throughout.
relevant_findings.psychiatric: Good insight and judgment. Alert and oriented. Normal memory. Pleasant affect.
